languages.text: "Номос решили. Мы уходим. Мы рады тому, что взяли у тебя, но дальше оставаться не можем и не хотим".
"Nomos have decided. We are leaving. We are glad to have received what we have from you, but we cannot and do not want to stay any longer."

languages.text: 「ノモスは決めた。我々は去る。我々はあなたから受け取ったものに感謝している。けれど、ここにはこれ以上留まることはできないし、留まりたくない」

languages.text: “诺莫斯已经做好了决定，我们要走了。你给我们的一切我们都非常高兴，但我们不能继续留在这里，也不想再这么做了。”
languages.original_text: "Nomos have decided. We are leaving. We are glad to have received what we have from you, but we cannot and do not want to stay any longer."

traits.locale_text: “诺莫斯已经做好了决定，我们要走了。你给我们的一切我们都非常高兴，但我们不能继续留在这里，也不想再这么做了。”

languages.text: "Nomos haben entschieden. Wir gehen. Wir sind froh, von Euch erhalten zu haben, was wir erhalten haben. Doch wir können und wollen nicht länger bleiben."
languages.original_text: "Nomos have decided. We are leaving. We are glad to have received what we have from you, but we cannot and do not want to stay any longer."

traits.locale_text: "Nomos haben entschieden. Wir gehen. Wir sind froh, von Euch erhalten zu haben, was wir erhalten haben. Doch wir können und wollen nicht länger bleiben."

languages.text: « Nous avons pris notre décision. Nous partons. Nous sommes heureux d'avoir reçu ce que vous nous avez donné, mais nous ne pouvons et ne voulons pas rester plus longtemps. »

languages.text: «Nomos ha tomado una decisión. Nos marchamos. Estamos contentos de haber recibido lo que queríamos, pero no podemos ni queremos permanecer aquí más tiempo».

languages.text: "Nomos kararını verdi. Gidiyoruz. Sizden elden ettiklerimiz için mutluyuz ancak daha fazla kalamayız, kalmak da istemiyoruz."
languages.original_text: "Nomos have decided. We are leaving. We are glad to have received what we have from you, but we cannot and do not want to stay any longer."

traits.locale_text: "Nomos kararını verdi. Gidiyoruz. Sizden aldıklarımızı elde ettiğimiz için mutluyuz ancak daha fazla kalamayız, kalmak da istemiyoruz."
